        <mxCell id="ctast" parent="1" value="POST /api/catalog/admin/upload-url&#xa;     body: { filename: video.mp4, content_type: video/mp4 }&#xa;     resp: { upload_url: https://storage.googleapis.com/...?X-Goog-Signature=...,&#xa;             object_name: videos/1748291234-video.mp4 }&#xa;     El cliente hace PUT directo a upload_url con el binario (valida 15 min)&#xa;&#xa;GET  /api/catalog/admin/download-url?object=videos/...mp4&#xa;     resp: { download_url: https://...?X-Goog-Signature=..., object_name }&#xa;     Usar como src del player de video (valida 1 hora)&#xa;&#xa;POST /api/catalog/admin/upload&#xa;     Content-Type: multipart/form-data, campo: file, max: 500 MB&#xa;     resp: { url: https://storage.googleapis.com/..., object_name }" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=0;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2A7A2A;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;" vertex="1">
